OL,7,FITV News understands a government
OL,8,Famendment to its flagship Hillsborough
OL,9,Flaw will no longer be put to MPs after
OL,10,Fobjections from campaigners and
OL,11,Fregional mayors.
OL,13,FAmendments proposed by the government
OL,14,Fon Wednesday brought spies within the
OL,15,Fscope of the legislation, subject to
OL,16,Fthe approval of the head of their
OL,17,Fservice.
