OL,7,FSpeaking Sunday morning, the Culture
OL,8,FSecretary Lisa Nandy denied the
OL,9,Fsecurity services would be exempt
OL,10,Funder the proposed amendment, telling
OL,11,Fthe BBC's Laura Kuenssberg: "I just
OL,12,Fwant to be really clear, the security
OL,13,Fservices won't be exempt.
OL,15,F"But there is a challenge that we've
OL,16,Fgot collectively, and the challenge is
OL,17,Fto make sure that this applies to the
OL,18,Fsecurity services without fear or
OL,19,Ffavour, that they can continue to do
OL,20,Ftheir jobs.
