OL,7,FObjections had been raised by regional
OL,8,Fmayors, including the Labour Mayor of
OL,9,FWest Yorkshire, Tracy Brabin, who said
OL,10,Fthat the duty of candour regarding the
OL,11,Fsecurity services was "vital" for
OL,12,Ffamilies who have campaigned for the
OL,13,FHillsborough Law.
OL,15,FMs Brabin told the BBC's Sunday With
OL,16,FLaura Kuenssberg programme that the
OL,17,Flegislation was "95% there" but
OL,18,F"without the trust and confidence of
OL,19,Fthe families, it's going to be very
OL,20,Fdifficult".
