OL,7,FIn a joint statement posted on X, the
OL,8,Fmayors added: "An important part of
OL,9,Fstrengthening the country's defences
OL,10,Fis establishing the truth at the
OL,11,Fearliest opportunity when things go
OL,12,Fwrong and that is why, if drafted
OL,13,Fcorrectly, the Hillsborough Law could
OL,14,Fcreate a culture in all public
OL,15,Fservices where that is the norm.
OL,17,F"As it stands, we believe the
OL,18,Fgovernment's amendment in relation to
OL,19,Fthe security services creates too
OL,20,Fbroad an opt-out and risks undermining
OL,21,Fthe spirit of the legislation.
